CI/CD Lifecycle & Concepts

1.Explain the complete CI/CD lifecycle and where Jenkins fits into each stage.
A full CI/CD pipeline contains:

Source Code Management (SCM)
Continuous Integration
Build & Artifact Packaging
Automated Testing
Static Analysis & Code Quality Checks
Artifact Storage (Artifact Repository)
Continuous Delivery (Staging Deployments)
