 first check the time range, correct index, and search syntax. Then I verify that the forwarder is running, inputs are correctly configured, and that the indexer is receiving data. I check Splunk internal logs, license usage, permissions, and the status of the search head/indexer. These checks help me isolate whether the issue is with ingestion, indexing, or search.

